This project builds upon concepts from the following academic works. We acknowledge
their contributions to the field and encourage proper citation when using Clearence
in academic or research contexts:

- Guarino et al. — "What Is an Ontology?"
- Sharma et al. — OG-RAG (hypergraph construction, dual retrieval)
- Bakker et al. — "Ontology Learning from Text" (sequential extraction)
- Smith & Proietti — "OWL 2 RL Logic Programming"
- OntoRAG (ICLR) — OntoGen taxonomy pipeline
- Gajderowicz et al. — "RAG and Ontologies"
- Huettemann et al. — "Ontology-based Search"

See README.md for full references and mapping to codebase layers.
